data.description: This home has a new idea - DIY KITCHEN  -  The owner was transferred at the time they were planning a new kitchen-  This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is located in Allison Park/Shaler school district.  The property has a great flow between the living room and the outdoor space making it a natural for entertaining.  Sliding doors from the kitchen to the large-flat back yard, which is fenced make it perfect for  pets or small children.  The downstairs game room features a fireplace and a seperate heat source.  The garage a heated two-car garage.
